ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:00:23.000Z","msg":"CLS，同人民日報表揚刀手有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>[濕L晒，你要驚]防毒濾棉濕哂水會打柴，請立即更換</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1506772\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1506772</a><br />\n整合左啲濾棉濕水嘅問題，大家幫手入去推比更多手足睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">為防TL;DR 先寫結論:<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n1. 外露濾棉如 2297/2097 + 單罐豬嘴3311K 等，如濕哂請即更換<br />\n2. 如501蓋 + 5N11/5P71 有外殼包下嘅，請打開檢查有無全濕<br />\n3. 內置濾棉嘅綜合濾罐 如60926/3系列，正路入水位唔多，但好睇實際有幾濕<br />\n4. 單純濾罐部份 如6006/3 系列，活性碳唔吸水，乾返應該唔大影響，有待實測<br />\n5. 雨天環境，重課可考慮502蓋 + 3M 7093 有殼防水式P100濾棉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:唔係呢方面專家，只係問人+整合資料，需要人實測"},{"pid":"7f8f0df0163e44725ac1ca8de516f6a6e1542d96","tid":1506973,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:01:21.000Z","msg":"黑社會也有愛國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1ee60daee3c9d580bfe610867e373639a6ae22","tid":1506973,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T04:03:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記者請重拾利君雅氣勢插追問10項注意 825警察用槍指你哋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1507002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1507002</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span>"},{"pid":"ffbca14a4cff37e71be7afe64f1ccfdb25e5510f","tid":1506973,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfd51d9d05272066df943c77a9874eec13c4af81","tid":1506973,"uid":204246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T03:38:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/